===Lucas&#x27;s formula===

Let &quot;n&quot; be odd, square-free and greater than 3. Then

:formula_57

for certain polynomials &quot;Un&quot;(&quot;z&quot;) and &quot;Vn&quot;(&quot;z&quot;) with integer coefficients, &quot;Un&quot;(&quot;z&quot;) of degree &quot;φ&quot;(&quot;n&quot;)/2, and &quot;Vn&quot;(&quot;z&quot;) of degree &quot;φ&quot;(&quot;n&quot;)/2 − 1. This can also be written

