===Sister Beiter conjecture===

The Sister Beiter conjecture is concerned with the maximal size (in absolute value) formula_61 of coefficients of &quot;ternary cyclotomic polynomials&quot; formula_62 where formula_63 are three odd primes.

== Cyclotomic polynomials over a finite field and over the -adic integers ==

Over a finite field with a prime number of elements, for any integer that is not a multiple of , the cyclotomic polynomial formula_13 factorizes into formula_65 irreducible polynomials of degree , where formula_14 is Euler&#x27;s totient function and is the multiplicative order of modulo . In particular, formula_13 is irreducible if and only if is a primitive root modulo, that is, does not divide , and its multiplicative order modulo is formula_68, the degree of formula_13.

These results are also true over the -adic integers, since Hensel&#x27;s lemma allows lifting a factorization over the field with elements to a factorization over the -adic integers.

