::&quot;u″&quot; = a signal that is correlated with the undesired signal &quot;u&quot;, but not correlated with &quot;g&quot; or &quot;g″&quot;,
::&quot;v&quot; = an undesired signal (typically random noise) not correlated with &quot;g&quot;, &quot;g″&quot;, &quot;u&quot;, &quot;u″&quot; or &quot;v″&quot;,
::&quot;v″&quot; = an undesired signal (typically random noise) not correlated with &quot;g&quot;, &quot;g″&quot;, &quot;u&quot;, &quot;u″&quot; or &quot;v&quot;.

